            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "# Test your friendship super skill\n\nWatch this picture for a minute. See if you can guess what the persons are thinking and feeling.\n\n\n\nINSERT PICTURE WHEN CLEARED WE CAN USE THAT ONE"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "I'm ready",
                "conversationId": "relationships-insideoutside-3",
                "sectionId": "2"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "alias": "2",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Now, ask yourself *how* you guessed what the persons are experiencing.\n\nIt is likely that you had to rely on how YOU would feel in the same situation. That’s what we all do. We rely on how we'd feel in the same situation when guessing how others feel."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Next",
                "conversationId": "relationships-insideoutside-3",
                "sectionId": "3"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "alias": "3",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Ask yourself, have you ever found out that a friend was really sad and it shocked you because you couldn't tell?\n\nHave you distanced yourself from another person because your mind-reading skills told you they didn't like you or didn't agree with you, but you never checked it out?\n\nHow about in reverse – has there been a time when you were not understood because people thought you looked ok?"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Go on",
                "conversationId": "relationships-insideoutside-3",
                "sectionId": "4"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "alias": "4",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "**Inside-outside vision** is about moving beyond blind guesses – it's learning to *check it out.*\n\nIt's time to change that. Here’s how:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
